xsa.name: gen3x16_xdma_1
xsa.description: This platform targets the Alveo U280 Data Center Accelerator Card. This high-performance acceleration platform features up to two channels of DDR4-2400 SDRAM which are instantiated as required by the user kernels for high fabric resource availability, HBM, the expanded partial reconfiguration flow for high fabric resource availability, and Xilinx DMA Subsystem for PCI Express with PCIe Gen3 x16 connectivity.
